<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Bella Thorne recently apologized to sex workers on OnlyFans, after her presence on the adult monetization platform caused some trouble.</p>

<p>But the former Disney Channel star is continuing to churn out some relatively mild content for the otherwise X-rated website.</p>

